{"tid":704131,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"新都城間天x名茶是咪on9","createTime":"2018-06-16T08:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T10:59:59.000Z","uid":113626,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9641413c0b7c2232f265d90f4828aeda782d72b8","tid":704131,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T08:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頭先走去買杯珍珠奶茶飲<br />\n本身凍既飲品, 係要之前開定d茶底嘆凍佢, 然而今日用<br />\n可能佢d凍既茶底已經用哂, 因為夏天多人飲凍野<br />\n佢地就直接用岩岩開出黎高溫既茶+凍既奶+冰, 放落攪伴機到攪, 沖成2杯珍珠奶茶出黎<br />\n買撚完一飲落去, 係飲緊水+珍珠<br />\n我飲一啖即刻拋撚左去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記者朋友如果要試的話就好快d去, 因為都係2個鐘之前到發生"},{"pid":"648edf07d27f166942bc792e2b7973fb5e5363a3","tid":704131,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T08:20:07.000Z","msg":"支那01記者快啲去"},{"pid":"8d38f3b9aad9f6ec6a8cd9563095349843321807","tid":704131,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T08:21:06.000Z","msg":"依家新都城除左天X之外<br />\n仲有邊到有得飲珠奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n貢茶都照殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（不過可惜執晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"75f4e20e0e8dc13264a684fed98e63c1ea522084","tid":704131,"uid":65433,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d38f3b9aad9f6ec6a8cd9563095349843321807","tid":704131,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T08:21:06.000Z","msg":"依家新都城除左天X之外<br />\n仲有邊到有得飲珠奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n貢茶都照殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（不過可惜執晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T08:22:33.000Z","msg":"去八方雲集飲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6b02c460d65bba0e958c4b834a9353427